  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Upcliff\" title=\"House Upcliff\"><img alt=\"House Upcliff.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/05/House_Upcliff.svg/50px-House_Upcliff.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/05/House_Upcliff.svg/75px-House_Upcliff.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/05/House_Upcliff.svg/100px-House_Upcliff.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Queen</span><br />Arwen Upcliff</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\"><img alt=\"House Arryn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/50px-House_Arryn.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/75px-House_Arryn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/100px-House_Arryn.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nQueen</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Upcliff\" title=\"House Upcliff\">House Upcliff</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">House Arryn</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nKing <a href=\"/index.php/Alester_II_Arryn\" title=\"Alester II Arryn\">Alester II Arryn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Arwen Upcliff</b> was a lady of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Upcliff\" title=\"House Upcliff\">House Upcliff</a> who married <a href=\"/index.php/Alester_II_Arryn\" title=\"Alester II Arryn\">Alester II Arryn</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_Mountain_and_Vale\" title=\"King of Mountain and Vale\">King of Mountain and Vale</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Arwen_Upcliff&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Arwen's marriage to <a href=\"/index.php/Alester_II_Arryn\" title=\"Alester II Arryn\">Alester II Arryn</a> brought the <a href=\"/index.php/Witch_Isle\" title=\"Witch Isle\">Witch Isle</a>, seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Upcliff\" title=\"House Upcliff\">House Upcliff</a>, into the realm of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">House Arryn</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Arwen_Upcliff&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Vale.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Last known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/Teora_Hunter\" title=\"Teora Hunter\">Teora Hunter</a> </b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> Queen consort of the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">kingdom of Mountain and Vale</a> </b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Next known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/Sharra_Arryn\" title=\"Sharra Arryn\">Sharra Arryn</a> </b>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404214056\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.089 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.305 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 728/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12442/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6424/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 763/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐ex